Blackheart stared at the scannes. "I see maybe 4 bases....this is 
complicated. A ship is airborn..but it seems not for long. Its a tripred 
ship. The predacons are obviously out matched but they seem to be 
surviving.....they must be worthy opponents." Blackheart had one 
weakness...the thrill of a challenge. "Send a comm to the Tripreds...if im 
not mistake thats Tyrael....I thought hed be dead by now. Tell them our 
position around the moon and that we wish to speak to them whenever their 
battle is over...I dont think we should intervene just yet...not until we 
know what were dealing with."

--part1_1c3.1566f58.2b009b80_boundary
